"title": "8289: joy, of the church",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8289: joy, of the church",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The church is to rejoice in the salvation brought about by Jesus Christ's faithful life and death, and by the power of his resurrection. Even in adversity, believers know the joy of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Joy at the coming of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:8-Luke2:11\">LUK 2:8–2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:27-John3:29\">JHN 3:27–3:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:56\">JHN 8:56</a></p>\n<h2>Joy as the hallmark of the kingdom of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:44\">MAT 13:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:17-Luke10:21\">LUK 10:17–10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:4-Luke15:10\">LUK 15:4–15:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:12-Matt18:14\">MAT 18:12–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34-John4:36\">JHN 4:34–4:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:20-John16:24\">JHN 16:20–16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:13\">JHN 17:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17-Rom14:18\">ROM 14:17–14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:16-1Thess5:18\">1TH 5:16–5:18</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ promises joy to his disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:9-John15:11\">JHN 15:9–15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:11–5:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:22-Luke6:23\">LUK 6:22–6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:20-John16:24\">JHN 16:20–16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:13\">JHN 17:13</a></p>\n<h3>Joy among believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46-Acts2:47\">ACT 2:46–2:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:1-Acts15:3\">ACT 15:1–15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:31-Rom15:32\">ROM 15:31–15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:3\">2CO 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:17-Phil2:18\">PHP 2:17–2:18</a></p>\n<h2>Joy experienced in relationship with Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:8-1Pet1:9\">1PE 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:7-John15:11\">JHN 15:7–15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22-Heb12:24\">HEB 12:22–12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:7\">REV 19:7</a></p>\n<h3>Joy experienced through conversion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:33-Acts16:34\">ACT 16:33–16:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:38-Acts8:39\">ACT 8:38–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:11\">ROM 5:11</a></p>\n<h2>Joy experienced even in adversity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:41\">ACT 5:41</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:12–4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:11–5:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:22-Luke6:23\">LUK 6:22–6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:4\">2CO 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1-2Cor8:2\">2CO 8:1–8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:7–12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:9\">2CO 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:17-Phil2:18\">PHP 2:17–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">COL 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:34\">HEB 10:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:3\">JAS 1:2–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:6\">1PE 1:3–1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Joy experienced by the apostles</h2>\n<h3>Joy because of the believers' faith and obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:19\">ROM 16:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:3-3John1:4\">3JN 1:3–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:4\">2CO 7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:23-Phil1:26\">PHP 1:23–1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:1\">PHP 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:5\">COL 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:19-1Thess2:20\">1TH 2:19–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:9\">1TH 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>Joy because of the believers' love and concern</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:7\">2CO 7:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:12-2Cor7:13\">2CO 7:12–7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:2\">PHP 2:1–2:2</a> <em>the Philippians' love for one another</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:7\">PHM 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>Joy because of the believers' partnership in the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:4-Phil1:6\">PHP 1:4–1:6</a></strong></p>",
